sequenceDiagram
    participant CS as Charging Station (OCTT)
    participant CSMS as CSMS (System Under Test)

    Note over CS,CSMS: Test Case: TC_G_03_CSMS
    Note over CS,CSMS: Change Availability EVSE - Operative to inoperative

    Note over CS,CSMS: 1. Execute Reusable State Unavailable for configured evseId

    CSMS->>CS: 1.1 ChangeAvailabilityRequest
    Note left of CSMS: operationalStatus = Inoperative<br/>evse.id = <Configured evseId>

    CS-->>CSMS: 1.2 ChangeAvailabilityResponse
    Note right of CS: status = Accepted

    CS->>CSMS: 1.3 StatusNotificationRequest
    Note right of CS: connectorStatus = Unavailable<br/>evseId = <Configured evseId>

    CSMS-->>CS: 1.4 StatusNotificationResponse

    CS->>CSMS: 1.5 NotifyEventRequest
    Note right of CS: trigger = Delta<br/>actualValue = "Unavailable"<br/>component.name = "Connector"<br/>variable.name = "AvailabilityState"

    CSMS-->>CS: 1.6 NotifyEventResponse
